# Recipe Sharing Platform - AI Rules

## Project Stack
- **Framework**: Next.js 16
- **UI**: React 19
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS v4
- **Language**: TypeScript (strict mode)

## Conventions
- Use path alias `@/*` for imports (e.g., `@/components/RecipeCard`)
- Prefer functional components and hooks
- Keep components small and single-purpose
- Use server components by default; add `"use client"` only when needed (interactivity, hooks, browser APIs)

## Code Quality
- Handle errors explicitly—avoid empty catch blocks
- Use meaningful variable and component names
- Prefer `const` over `let`; avoid `var`
